column5: You'll love this comfortable, nice home in Katy's best area. Sophisticated, spacious, and close to quiet, shady park. Safe neighborhood in desirable location. Close to Westpark Tollway and Grand Parkway with easy commute to Houston. Super clean and pristine, quality linens and well stocked kitchen. Newly furnished and with all conveniences. Spacious backyard, garage available for parking your car.
